profile:
Discover the Finest in Home Cleaning. 

The opulence of a sparkling window. The richness of a clean floor. 

This holiday season, let your loved ones unwrap the gift of a home well cleaned. We would love nothing more than to be at your service.

Imagine coming home and you can’t help but smell just how fresh it is. Everything around you is so clean and perfectly arranged that you feel the stress of your day melt away with each step. 

You’ll have peace of mind knowing your home has been cleaned using the highest quality cleaning supplies, a 47-point checklist, and a HEPA filter vacuum to trap microscopic particles as small as 0.1 microns. A vacuum as perfectionist as the cleaners - it even has a laser so you know it’s spotless. 

Of course you’ll be elated. But what if you’re not? Let us know and we’ll return same-day and compensate you for your time.

profile:
When you're looking for Kitchener maid service, look at MaidPro. We're making ON shine, one house at a time, serving, the entire Kitchener area.

MaidPro is Kitchener's premier cleaning service. Whether you want weekly, bi-weekly or just a one-time house cleaning, we'll design your maid service around your needs. We understand that hiring a maid service can be a big decision, and we will work with you to ensure your 'hot spots' are cleaned the way you want them done, on time, every time.
